{"tid":2092602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Eason最新慈善演唱會 11/7橫跨日出日落舉行","createTime":"2020-07-03T09:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:22:54.000Z","uid":274858,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f0230fc5f708ade61119eb548ee70edf8702fb","tid":2092602,"uid":274858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZHRMrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZHRMrv.jpg&h=3c76925a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日（3/7）「香港現場演出及制作行業協會」舉行發布會，宣布Eason陳奕迅將在7月11日舉行「Live is so much better with Music Eason Chan Charity Concert」慈善音樂會。Eason不但不收酬勞，更邀請眾多音樂界好友一起設計演出內容。<br />\n<br />\nEason今日以短片形式分享感受，他指：「日出日落便是一天，無論今天怎樣困難，明天太陽還會升起，希望大家有信心、有勇氣，相互扶持共渡難關。」音樂會以「日出日落」為主題，將分為早上6時及黃昏5時兩段時間舉行，並將在「香港演出及制作行業協會」官方平台，及全球各個電視台及網上平台直播。<br />\n<br />\n終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次中環把聲靚到"},{"pid":"e1126ed438a37b8a0d26e35c5550c6580ff113a1","tid":2092602,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"分兩段有啲on9 <br />\n你話由朝早唱到夜晚就話姐"},{"pid":"869060d880a0126312604e1ce94a0fccf2abdf26","tid":2092602,"uid":107913,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"早上六點 for廢老睇?"},{"pid":"00cb548fca65efccdb1c73e84e35a28335a4d955","tid":2092602,"uid":140834,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"單春支持武漢不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ea5bba06a0746b8f9a5bf3554565f4ed2426d7","tid":2092602,"uid":299311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"太陽照常升起.jpg"},{"pid":"3e01c6bb9b175535b16fa57a5a1674957d0268d1","tid":2092602,"uid":107913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"可能知道冇左黃色市場 索性遷就藍絲廢老"},{"pid":"5795b752686db7172f0767e6ef671eb931323a78","tid":2092602,"uid":55309,"l